OL,3,CEx-England cricketer's daughter would
OL,4,Chave survived with quicker care `
OL,5,Ccoroner
OL,7,FThe daughter of a former England
OL,8,Fcricket star would not have died from
OL,9,Fsepsis had she received more prompt
OL,10,Furgent medical care, a coroner has
OL,11,Fruled.
OL,13,FBethan James, 21, the daughter of
OL,14,Fformer Glamorgan and England batter
OL,15,FSteve James, died on February 8 2020
OL,16,Fjust a few hours after being admitted
OL,17,Fto hospital.
