OL,5,Ccoroner
OL,7,FA post-mortem examination found she
OL,8,Fdied of sepsis and pneumonia, with
OL,9,Fcomplications caused by Crohn's
OL,10,Fdisease.
OL,12,FAn inquest in Pontypridd heard Ms
OL,13,FJames, a journalism student at the
OL,14,FUniversity of South Wales, died while
OL,15,Fbeing treated at the University
OL,16,FHospital of Wales (UHW) in Cardiff.
OL,18,FShe had suffered with gastrointestinal
OL,19,Fissues for most of her life and had
OL,20,Fbeen diagnosed with Crohn's disease in
OL,21,F2019.
