OL,3,CEx-England cricketer's daughter would
OL,4,Chave survived with quicker care `
OL,5,Ccoroner
OL,7,FFollowing complaints of being short of
OL,8,Fbreath, Ms James was given antibiotics
OL,9,Ffor community-acquired pneumonia in
OL,10,Flate January.
OL,12,FHer condition continued to decline,
OL,13,Fand she was taken to Llandough
OL,14,FHospital twice before she was admitted
OL,15,Fto UHW on the evening of February 8,
OL,16,Fthe inquest was told.
OL,18,FPatricia Morgan, area coroner for
OL,19,FSouth Wales Central, said there were
OL,20,Fdelays in the treatment to Ms James
OL,21,Fafter she arrived at the hospital.
