OL,3,CEx-England cricketer's daughter would
OL,4,Chave survived with quicker care `
OL,5,Ccoroner
OL,7,FIn recording a narrative conclusion,
OL,8,Fshe said the ambulance crew had failed
OL,9,Fto issue a pre-alert to the hospital
OL,10,Fof how sick she was, which would have
OL,11,Fresulted in her immediate admittance
OL,12,Fto the resuscitation area of the
OL,13,Femergency department.
OL,15,F"I find that the lack of pre-alert to
OL,16,Frecess resulted in a lack of advanced
OL,17,Fknowledge of Bethan's condition and
OL,18,Fconsequently no efforts made to secure
OL,19,Fa bed for her in the resus area," she
OL,20,Fsaid.
