OL,3,CEx-England cricketer's daughter would
OL,4,Chave survived with quicker care `
OL,5,Ccoroner
OL,7,F"There's no clinical staff waiting for
OL,8,FBethan when she arrived in the way
OL,9,Fthat would have occurred had a pre-
OL,10,Falert been issued.
OL,12,F"It resulted in an unwillingness of
OL,13,Fthe recess lead nurse to become
OL,14,Finvolved in the initial decision
OL,15,Fmaking, instead directing them to the
OL,16,Fmajor assessment nurse in line with
OL,17,Fadmission procedure for those not
OL,18,Fdeemed to meet the issues criteria for
OL,19,Fresus.
