OL,3,CEx-England cricketer's daughter would
OL,4,Chave survived with quicker care `
OL,5,Ccoroner
OL,7,F"It resulted in time being taken to
OL,8,Ftriage back then and a further
OL,9,Fhandover being provided to hospital
OL,10,Fstaff in the majors area.
OL,12,F"It's all been a delay, which in my
OL,13,Fview, would not have been the case had
OL,14,Fthe pre-alert been issued, critically
OL,15,Fresulting in a delay of approximately
OL,16,Fone hour in obtaining the lactate
OL,17,Freading for Bethan."
