OL,7,FThe coroner said she had heard
OL,8,Fevidence from doctors working at the
OL,9,FUHW, as well as expert witness Dr
OL,10,FChris Danbury, and said she was "more
OL,11,Fpersuaded" by his evidence.
OL,13,F"Dr Danbury expressed a strong view
OL,14,Fthat the outcome would have been
OL,15,Fdifferent for Bethan if she had been
OL,16,Fsubject to a pre-alert and admitted
OL,17,Finto resus immediately," she said.
