OL,3,CEx-England cricketer's daughter would
OL,4,Chave survived with quicker care `
OL,5,Ccoroner
OL,7,F"I am therefore more persuaded by Dr
OL,8,FDanbury's opinion on treatment options
OL,9,Fand whether earlier treatment would
OL,10,Fhave made a difference.
OL,12,F"I find that if earlier recognition
OL,13,Fand prompt action in response to
OL,14,FBethan's condition upon attendance by
OL,15,Fambulance services had occurred, this
OL,16,Fwould have resulted in a pre-alert to
OL,17,Fthe emergency department.
