OL,4,Chave survived with quicker care `
OL,5,Ccoroner
OL,7,F"This would have resulted in direct
OL,8,Fadmission into resus, with clinical
OL,9,Fstaff waiting for her, quicker triage
OL,10,Fprocess, and earlier treatment would
OL,11,Fhave and ought to have commenced.
OL,13,F"Earlier lactate treatments would have
OL,14,Fbeen available, and the involvement of
OL,15,Fthe specialists would have and ought
OL,16,Fto have occurred at an earlier stage.
