OL,7,F"On balance I find that Bethan would
OL,8,Fnot have died."
OL,10,FAddressing her parents, the coroner
OL,11,Fsaid: "It's been five years plus since
OL,12,FBethan passed away and I don't doubt
OL,13,Fthat the pain is still as strong as it
OL,14,Fwas back then.
OL,16,F"I'm sure the evidence in relation to
OL,17,FBethan's passing will have resurrected
OL,18,Fa lot of your sad memories so I just
OL,19,Fwant to express my condolences on
OL,20,Fbehalf of myself and the coroner's
OL,21,Fservice."
